e flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u2714\ufe0f <strong>No waiting \u2013 just pure strategy</strong> \u2013 No idle mechanics, just smart planning and satisfying progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you build the perfect production chain and <strong>claim the crown?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udc51 <strong>Play now and become a master of optimization!</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738754571","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738754571","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738754571","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191410/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738754571","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":2712690,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>For The Crown \u2013 The Addictive Puzzle-Building Game</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfc6 <strong>Winner of &quot;Best Game Programming Project SAE 2023&quot;</strong> (See the award on YouTube)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Build production chains, optimize resource flows, and grow your empire! <strong>For The Crown</strong> is a <strong>puzzle-building game</strong> where every decision matters. Connect buildings, fine-tune your economy, and <strong>turn simple resources into gold</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udca1 <strong>Why you won\u2019t be able to stop playing:</strong><br>\u2714\ufe0f <strong>Easy to pick up, fun to mast